---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="persona-blog">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Hey, I'm persona</h1>
  
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
    A Security Researcher, which is a fancy way of saying I get paid to find bugs in smart contracts. 
    This site is my personal notebook for things I'm learning, tools I'm building with Rust and my ongoing experiments with fuzzing.
  </p>

  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Latest projects</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
      This is a collection of my open-source tools and libraries. Each one started as an experiment to learn something new or to fix a problem I had.
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      <li>
        <a href="/docs/cmdtest" class="font-semibold hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
          cmdtest:
        </a>
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"> CLI testing for Zig</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/docs/xdgdir" class="font-semibold hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
          xdgdir:
        </a>
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"> A tiny Rust crate for XDG directories</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/docs/envfmt" class="font-semibold hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
          envfmt:
        </a>
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"> Expand environment variables in strings</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Latest posts</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
      This blog is my public notebook. It's where I document what I'm doing, share solutions to bugs, and write down my thoughts on Rust and other tech.
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-4">
      <li>
        <article>
          <h3 class="font-semibold">
            <a href="/blog/example-post" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
              Security Audit Review: A Reward Accounting Bug in Stakehouse
            </a>
          </h3>
          <time class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">March 4, 2026</time>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
            I'm reviewing past audit findings to build a personal checklist for future audits.
          </p>
        </article>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-6 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">
      Show all posts →
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
